Generic single-database configuration for Flask-Migrate.

To create a new migration:
```
flask db migrate -m "Description of changes"
```

To apply migrations:
```
flask db upgrade
```

To downgrade:
```
flask db downgrade
```Generic single-database configuration for Flask-Migrate.

To initialize the migrations directory:
```
flask db init
```

To create a new migration:
```
flask db migrate -m "Description of changes"
```

To apply migrations:
```
flask db upgrade
```

To downgrade:
```
flask db downgrade
```